en_900674_0	Brigadier A.L Illangakoon took over office as the 12th Director, Directorate of Provost during a simple ceremony at the Army Headquarters on Wednesday (5).
en_900674_1	Amid religious observances, he placed his signature symbolically for a document and accepted the new appointment.
en_900674_2	Officers and Other Ranks of the Directorate of Provost at the Army Headquarters were present during the occasion.
en_900674_3	Before this appointment, he served as the Centre Commandant of Sri Lanka Corps of Military Police.
